name: Evadne
description:
"Evadne" from The "Insight" Collection by Armin Jabbarehasl is now available on hic et nunc. 
 
"Evadne" is a (3400px X  3400px) Image which is made out of simple photographs from different objects to provide a generative piece. 
 
The Owner will receive the "Evadne"'s High Resolution(3400px X 3400px) File.
